The paper proposes a novel neural network and training algorithm for multi-task learning, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of reinforcement learning (cs.AI) and neural networks such as fully-connected and convolutional layers (cs.NE, cs.CV). The experiments are conducted on image datasets such as MNIST, mini-imagenet, and CIFAR-100 (cs.CV), and the paper discusses the potential applications of the proposed model in natural language processing (cs.CL).
